result.name: Diversity data for Wild Emmer Wheat Sequencing Project
result.description: This is the variant data supporing the wild emmer wheat genome submission consisting of 33 WEW accessions and 31 DEW accessions presented in Science 357 (6346), 93-97. The samples in this project were aligned to Zavitan reference genome (wild emmer). The project leader is Assaf Distelfeld from The Institute for Cereal Crops Improvement, Tel Aviv University. Variant data was analyzed at Kansas State University.
